# Outlier Assessment

The PCA generated in this SOP is exploratory.

Potential outliers may be visualized separately to facilitate interpretation of the overall dataset structure.

Outliers should not be automatically removed at this stage.

Sample exclusion should only be considered after subsequent filtering steps and careful evaluation of:

* QC metrics
* PCA behavior after filtering
* Experimental records
* Instrumental performance

